      "design_plan": "Placeholder visual only. Narrative goal: briefly signal that this row is about a risky action being stopped by containment. Hero metaphor: a blocked boundary wall between a local agent box on the left and a restricted zone on the right, with a simple guardrail badge in the middle. Main objects: 1) title at top saying Working on visual, 2) subtitle noting risky action and containment, 3) left local agent card, 4) center boundary/stop marker labeled MxC / Guardrail, 5) right restricted target card. Layout: title and subtitle centered near top; left card around x 140 y 220; center stop/boundary around x 480 y 270; right card around x 650 y 220. Colors: scene background $background, title $title, subtitle $subtitle, cards $surface with $border, key warning accent via $warning, labels $foreground and $muted. Motion beats: quick fade in title, then left card, then center blocked boundary, then right target with a short arrow that appears and stops before crossing the boundary."
